hadiths[34]{hadithnumber,text}:
3156,main Jaabir bin Zaid aur Amr bin Aus ke sath betha hua tha to un donon buzurgon se Bajaala ne bayan kya ke 70 hijri mein jis saal Musab bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne Basra walon ke sath Haj kya tha. zamzam ki seedhiyon ke paas unhon-ne bayan kya tha ke main Ahnaf bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha Juz-bin-Muaawiya ka kaatib tha. to wafat se aik saal pahley umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik khat hamarey paas aaya ke jis paarsii ne apni mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) aurat ko biwi banaya ho to unko juda kar do aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne paarsiyon se jiziya nahi liya tha.
3157,lekin jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne gawahi di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hijr ke paarsiyon se jiziya liya tha (to wo bhi leney lagey they).
3158,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Ubaida-bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Bahrain jiziya wsool karne ke liye bheja tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bahrain ke logon se suleh ki thi aur un par Alaa-bin-Hizramii (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hakim banaya tha. jab abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Bahrain ka maal lekar aaey to Ansar ko malum ho gaya ke abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) aagey hain. chunanche fajr ki Namaz sab logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padha chukey to log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein dekh kar muskuraaey aur farmaya ke mera khayal hai ke tum ne sun liya hai ke abu-Ubaida kuchh lekar aaey hain? Ansar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ji haan, ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumhen khushkhabri ho, aur us cheez ke liye tum pur-ummeed raho. jis se tumhen khushi hogi, lekin Allah ki qasam! main tumharey barey mein mohtaajii aur faqr se nahi dartaa. mujhey agar khof hai to is baat ka kuchh duniya ke darwazey tum par is tarah khol diye jaeinge jaisey tum se pahley logon par khol diye gaey they, to aisa na ho ke tum bhi unki tarah aik doosrey se jalney lago aur ye jalnaa tum ko bhi isi tarah tabah kar de jaisa ke pahley logon ko kya tha."
3159,"kuffaar se jang ke liye umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne faujon ko) Faaris ke) badey badey shehron ki taraf bheja tha. (jab lashkar qaadsiya pahuncha aur ladai ka nateeja musalmanon ke haq mein niklaa) to harmuzaan (Shoster ka haakim) Islam ley aaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se farmaya ke main tum se un (mumaalik Faaris wghaira) par fauj bhejney ke silsiley mein mashwara chahta hun (ke pahley un teen maqaamon Faaris , Asfahaan aur aazarbaaijaan mein kahan se ladai shuru ki jaey) usne kaha ji haan! us mulk ki misal aur is mein rehney waley Islam dushman baashindon ki misal aik parindey jaisi hai jiska sar hai, 2 bazu hain. agar uska aik bazu tod diya jaey to wo apne donon paon par aik bazu aur aik sar ke sath khada reh sakta hai. agar doosra bazu bhi tod diya jaey to donon paon aur sar ke sath khada reh sakta hai. lekin agar sar tod diya jaey to donon paon donon bazu aur sar sab be-kaar reh jata hai. to sar to Kisraa hai, aik bazu qaisar hai aur doosra faaras! isliye aap musalmanon ko hukm de dein ke pahley wo Kisraa par hamla karein aur Bakr-bin-Abdullaah aur Ziyad bin-Jubair donon ne bayan kya ke unse Jubair-bin-Hayi ne bayan kya ke hamein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (jihad ke liye) bulaya aur Naumaan-bin-Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ko hamara ameer muqarrar kya. jab ham dushman ki sar zameen ( nahaawand (ke qareeb pahunchey to Kisraa ka aik afsar chalis (40) hazaar ka lashkar sath liye huey hamarey muqable ke liye badha . phir aik tarjuman ne aa kar kaha ke tum mein se koi aik shakhs ( maamlaat par) guftgu kare. Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( musalmanon ki numaaindagii ki aur) farmaya ke jo tumharey mataalbaat (maangein) hon, unhein bayan karo. us ne puchha aakhir tum log ho kon ? Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham Arab ke rehney waley hain, ham intihai bd-bakhtiyon aur museebaton mein mubtala they. bhook ki shiddat mein ham chamdey, aur guthliyaan choosaa kartey they. oon aur baal hamari poshak thi aur pattharon aur darakhton ki ham ibadat kya kartey they. hamari museebatein isi tarah qaaim thin ke aasman aur zameen ke rab ne, jiska zikr apni tamam azmat w jalaal ke sath buland hai. hamari taraf hamari hi tarah (ke insani aadaat w khususiyaat rakhney wala) aik Nabi bhejaa. ham uske bap aur maan ko jantey hain. Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham tum se us waqt tak jang kartey rahen. jab tak tum sirf Allah akeley ki ibadat na karne lago . ya phir Islam na qabool karne ki sura mein jiziya dena qabool kar lo aur hamarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apne rab ka ye paigham bhi pahunchaya hai ke (Islam ke liye ladtey huey) jihad mein hamara jo aadmi bhi qatl kya jaeyga wo aisi jannat mein jaeyga jo usney kabhi nahi dekhi aur jo log ham mein se zinda baqi reh jaeinge wo (fatah hasil karke) tum par Hakim bin sakengey (mugheera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye guftgu tamam karke Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ladai shuru karo)."
3160,"tum ko to Allah paak aisi kai ladaaiyon main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik rakh chuka hai. aur us ne (ladaaii mein der karne par) tum ko na sharminda kya na zaleel kya aur main to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ladai mein maujood tha. aap ka qaayeda tha agar subah sawerey ladai shuru na kartey aur din chadh jata to us waqt tak thahrey rahtey ke suraj dhal jaey, hawaaein chalney lagein, namazon ka waqt aan pahunchey."
3161,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham jange-Tabook mein Sharik they. iila ke Hakim (Yuhanna-bin-Rooba) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik safaid khachchar bheja aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey aik chadar bataur poshaak ke aur aik tahreer ke zariey uske mulk par usey hi Hakim baqi rakha.
3162,"maine Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha, (jab wo zakhmi huey) aap se ham ne arz kya tha ke hamein koi wasiiyat keejiye! to aap ne farmaya ke main tumhen Allah Taala ke ahad ki (jo tum ne zimmiyon se kya hai) wasiiyat karta hun (ke uski hifazat mein kotahi na karnaa) kyonke wo tumharey Nabi ka zimma hai aur tumharey ghar walon ki rozii hai (ke jiziye ke rupye se tumharey baal-bachchon ki guzraan hoti hai)."
3163,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko bulaayaa, taake Bahrain mein unke liye kuchh zameen likh dein. lekin unhon-ne arz kya ke nahin! Allah ki qasam! (hamein usi waqt wahan zameen inayat farmaaiye) jab itni zameen hamarey bhai Quraish (muhaajireen) ke liye bhi aap likhein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tak Allah ko manzoor hai ye rozi-rotii unko bhi (yani Quraish walon ko) miltii rahegii.'' lekin Ansar yahi israar kartey rahe ke Quraish walon ke liye bhi sanadein likh dijiye. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar se farmaya ke mere baad tum ye dekhogey ke dusron ko tum par tarjeeh di jaeygi, lekin tum sabr se kaam lenaa, yahan tak ke tum aakhir mein mujh se aa kar milo (jang aur fasaad na karnaa)."
3164,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke agar hamarey paas Bahrain se rupya aaya, to main tumhen itna , itna , itna ( teen lap ( doonga . phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur uske baad Bahrain ka rupya aaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne agar kisi se koi dene ka wada kya ho to wo hamarey paas aaey. chunanche main hazir hua aur arz kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke agar Bahrain ka rupya hamarey yahan aaya to main tumhen itnaa, itna aur itna doonga. is par unhon-ne farmaya ke achchha aik lap bharo, maine aik lap bharii, to unhon-ne farmaya ke usey gino, maine ginaa to panch so tha, phir unhon-ne mujhey dedh hazaar inayat farmaya,"
3165,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan Bahrain se khiraaj ka rupya aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey masjid mein phaila do, Bahrain ka wo maal un tamam amwaal mein sabse zyada tha jo ab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan aa chukey they. itney mein Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur kehney lagey ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey bhi inayat farmaiye (main zere-baar hon yani mujh par qarz hai) kyonke maine (badr ke mauqe par) apna bhi fidya ada kya tha aur Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ka bhi ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha ley lijiye . chunanche unhon-ne apne kapdey mein rupya bhar liya ( lekin uthaya na ja sakaa) to usmein se kam karne lagey. lekin kam karne ke baad bhi na uth saka to arz kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi ko hukm dein ke uthaney mein meri madad karey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa nahi ho sakta , unhon-ne kaha ke phir aap khud hi uthwa dein. farmaya ke ye bhi nahi ho sakta. phir Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein se kuchh kam kya, lekin is par bhi na utha sakey to kaha ke kisi ko hukm dijiye ke wo utha de, farmaya ke nahi aisa nahi ho sakta, unhon-ne kaha phir aap hi utha dein, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye bhi nahi ho sakta. aakhir usmein se unhein phir kam karna padaa aur tab kahin ja ke usey apne kaandhey par utha sakey aur lekar janey lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tak unhein barabar dekhtey rahe, jab tak wo hamari nazron se chhup na gaey. unke hirs par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tajjub farmaya aur aap us waqt tak wahan se na uthey jab tak wahan aik dirham bhi baqi raha."
3166,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne kisi zimmii ko (naahaq) qatl kya wo jannat ki khushbu bhi na pa sakega. halanke jannat ki khushbu chalis (40) saal ki raah se soonghii ja sakti hai.''
3167,"ham abhi masjide-Nabawi mein maujood they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, aur farmaya ke yahudiyon ki taraf chalo. chunanche ham rawaana huey aur jab baital-Midraas (yahoodiyon ka madrasa) pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke Islam lao to salamati ke sath rahogey aur samajh lo ke zameen Allah aur aur uske rasool ki hai. aur mera irada hai ke tumhen is mulk se nikal dun, phir tum mein se agar kisi ki jaaidaad ki qeemat aaey to usey bech daley. agar tum is par taiyaar nahi ho, to tumhen malum hona chahiye ke zameen Allah aur uske rasool hi ki hai."
3168,"aap ne jumerat ke din ka zikr kartey huey kaha, tumhen malum hai ke jumerat ka din , haaye ! ye kon sa din hai? iske baad wo itna roey ke unke aansuon se kankariyaan tar ho gain . Saeed ne kaha maine arz kya, ya abu-Abbaas ! jumerat ke din se kya matlab hai? unhon-ne kaha ke isi din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki takleef ( marzul-maut ( mein shiddat paida hui thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke mujhey ( likhney ka ( aik kaaghaz de do taake main tumharey liye aik aisi kitab likh jaun, jiske baad tum kabhi gumrah na ho. is par logon ka ikhtilaf ho gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi farmaya ke Nabi ki maujoodgii mein jhagadnaa ghair-munaasib hai, doosrey log kehney lagey, bhala kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) be-kaar baatein farmaaengey. achchha, phir poochh lo, ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey meri haalat par chhod do, kyonke is waqt main jis aalim mein hun, wo us se behtar hai jiski taraf tum mujhey bula rahe ho. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baton ka hukm farmaya, ke mushrikon ko jazeera Arab se nikal dena aur wufood ke sath isi tarah khaatir tawaazoh ka mamla karnaa, jis tarah main kya karta tha. teesri baat kuchh bhalii si thi, ya to Saeed ne usko bayan na kya, ya mein bhool gaya. Sufiyan ne kaha ye jumla ( teesri baat kuchh bhalii si thi) Sulaiman ahwal ka kalam hai."
3169,"jab khaibar fateh hua to (yahoodiyon ki taraf se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bakri ka ya aisey gosht ka hadiya pesh kya gaya jis mein zahar tha. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jitney Yahudi yahan maujood hain unhein mere paas jama karo, chunanche wo sab aa gaey. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dekho, main tum se aik baat poochhoonga. kya tum log saheeh-saheeh jawab doge? sab ne kaha ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, tumharey bap kon they? unhon-ne kaha ke fulaan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum jhoot boltey ho, tumharey bap to falan they. sab ne kaha ke aap sach farmatey hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar main tum se aik aur baat poochhoon to tum sahi waqia bayan kar doge? sab ne kaha ji haan, aey abul-Qaasim! aur agar ham jhoot bhi bolengey to aap hamari jhoot ko isi tarah pakad lengey jis tarah aap ne abhi hamarey bap ke barey mein hamarey jhoot ko pakad liya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad malum farmaya ke dozakh mein janey waley kon log hongey? unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh dinon ke liye to ham usmein dakhil ho jaeinge lekin phir aap log hamari jagah dakhil kar diye jaengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum usmein barbad raho, Allah gawah hai ke ham tumhari jagah usmein kabhi dakhil nahi kiye jaengey. phir aap ne malum farmaya ke agar main tum se koi baat poochhoon to kya tum mujh se sahi waqia bata doge? is martaba bhi unhon-ne yahi kaha ke haan! aey abul-Qaasim! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum kya ke kya tum ne us bakri ke gosht mein zahar milaya hai? unhon-ne kaha ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tum ne aisa kyon kya? unhon-ne kaha ke hamara maqsad ye tha ke agar aap jhootey hain ( nabwooat mein) to hamein aaraam mil jaeyga aur agar aap waqei Nabi hain to ye zahar aapko koi nuqsan na pahuncha sakega."
3170,"maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se duaae-qunoot ke barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya ke rukoo se pahley honii chaahiye, maine arz kya ke falan sahib (Muhammad-bin Siiriin) to kehtey hain ke aap ne kaha tha ke rukoo ke baad hoti hai, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha tha ke unhon-ne ghalat kaha hai. phir unhon-ne ham se ye hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak rukoo ke baad dua qunoot ki thi aur aap ne usmein banu-Sulaim ke qabeelon ke haq mein baddua ki thi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chalis (40) ya 70 Quran ke aalim sahaba ki aik jamat , rawi ko shak tha, mushrekeen ke paas bheji thi, lekin banu-Sulaim ke log ( jinka sardaar Aamir-bin-Tufail tha) unke aadey aaey aur unko mar dala. halanke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unka muaahida tha. (lekin unhon-ne daghaa di) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi maamle par itna ranjeeda aur ghamgeen nahi dekha jitna un sahaba ki shahadat par aap ranjeeda they."
3171,"fateh Makka ke mauqe par main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui (Makka mein) maine dekha ke aap ghusl kar rahe they aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap ki sahibzadi parda kiye huey thin. maine aapko salam kya, to aap ne malum farmaya ke kon saahiba hain? maine arz kya ke main umme-Haanii-binte-abii-Taalib hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aao achi aaiin, Umme-Hani ! phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl se farigh huey to aap ne khadey ho kar aath (8) rakaat chasht ki Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf aik kapda jism at'har par lapetey huey they. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri maa ke betey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke wo aik shakhs ko jisey main panah de chuki hon, qatl kiye baghair nahi rahengey. ye shakhs Hubaira ka falan ladka ( ja'ada ( hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Umme-Hani ! jisey tum ne panah di, usey hamari taraf se bhi panah hai. Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ye waqt chasht ka tha."
3172,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamarey samney khutba diya, jis mein farmaya ke kitabullah aur us waraq mein jo kuchh hai, iske siwa aur koi kitab ( ehkaam shariiat ki) aisi hamarey paas nahi jisey ham padhtey hon, phir aap ne farmaya ke usmein zakhmon ke qisaas ke ehkaam hain aur diyat mein diye janey waley ki umr ke ehkaam hain aur ye ke Madina haram hai eir pahaadii se falan ( ahad pahaadii ( tak. isliye jis shakhs ne koi nai baat ( shariiat ke andar dakhil ki) ya kisi aisey shakhs ko panah di to is par Allah , malaaika aur insan sab ki laanat hai, na uski koi farz ibadat qabool hogi aur na nafl aur ye bayan hai jo londi ghulam apne Malik ke siwa kisi doosrey ko Malik banaey is par bhi isi tarah ( laanat ( hai. aur musalman muslmaan sab barabar hain har aik ka zimma yaksan hai. to jis shakhs ne kisi musalman ki panah mein (jo kisi kaafir ko di gaee ho ( dakhal andazi ki to is par bhi isi tarah laanat hai."
3173,"Abdullah-bin Sehal aur mahiisa bin Masood bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey. un dinon ( khaibar ke yahudiyon se musalmanon ki) suleh thi. phir donon hazraat ( khaibar pahunch kar apne apney kaam ke liye) juda ho gaey. iske baad mahiisa (Raziallahu anhu) Abdullah-bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey to kya dekhtey hain ke wo khoon mein lath-path hain. kisi ne unko qatl kar daalaa, khair mahiisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dafn kar diya. phir Madina aaey, iske baad Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Sahal (Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhaaii) aur Masood ke donon sahibzadey mahiisa aur Huwesa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, guftgu Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne shuru ki, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke jo tum logon mein umr mein badey hon wo baat karein. Abdur-Rehman sabse kam Umr they, wo chup ho gaey aur mahiisa aur huwesa ne baat shuru ki. aap ne malum kya, kya tum log is par qism kha saktey ho, ke jis shakhs ko tum qaatil keh rahe ho is par tumhara haq Sabit ho sakey. un logon ne arz kya ke ham aik aisey mamley mein kis tarah qism kha saktey hain jis ko ham ne khud apni aankhon se na dekha ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir kya yahood tumharey da'wey se apni Bara't (Tauba) apni taraf se pachaas qasmein kha karke kar dein? un logon ne arz kya ke kuffaar ki qasmon ka ham kis tarah eitibaar kar saktey hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apne paas se unko diyat ada kar di."
3174,Hiraql (farmaanrawaaey Rome (mojooda Itly)) ne unhein Quraish ke qafley ke sath bula bheja (ye log Sham (Syria) us zamaney mein tijarat ki gharaz se gaey huey they.) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Sufiyan se (Suleh Hudaibiya mein) Quraish ke kaafiron ke muqaddime mein suleh ki thi.
3175,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaadoo kar diya gaya tha. to kuchh baar aisa hota ke aap samajhtey ke maine falan kaam kar liya hai. halanke aap ne wo kaam na kya hota.
3176,"mein jange-Tabook ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aap us waqt chamdey ke aik khemey mein tashrif farma they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke qiyamat ki chh nishaniyan shumaar kar lo, meri maut, phir baitul-maqdis ki fatah, phir aik wabaa jo tum mein shiddat se phailegii jaisey bakriyon mein taaoon phail jata hai. phir maal ki kasarat us darja mein hogi ke aik shakhs so Dinar bhi agar kisi ko dega to is par bhi wo naraz hoga. phir fitna itna tabah kun aam hoga ke Arab ka koi ghar baqi na rahega jo uski lapet mein na aa gaya hoga. phir suleh jo tumharey aur bani al-Asfar (Rome ke eisaaii) ke darmyan hogi, lekin wo daghaa karengey aur aik azeem lashkar ke sath tum par chadhai karengey. usmein usi jhandey hongey aur har jhandey ke ma-tehet baara hazaar fauj hogi (yani nau (9) laakh sath hazaar fauj se wo tum par hamla aawar hongey)."
3177,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (hijjatul-wadaa se pahley waley Haj ke mauqe par) dasween Zil-Hijja ke din kuchh doosrey logon ke sath mujhey bhi Mina mein ye elaan karne bheja tha ke us saal ke baad koi mushrik Haj karne na aaey aur koi shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf nangey ho kar na karey aur Haje-akbar ka din dasween taareekh Zil-Hijja ka din hai. usey Haje-Akbar isliye kaha gaya ke log ( Umra ko) Haj asghar kehney lagey they, to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us saal mushrikon se jo ahad liya tha usey wapas kar diya, aur doosrey saal Hijjatul-wada mein jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj kya to koi mushrik Sharik nahi hua."
3178,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, char aadatein aisi hain ke agar ye charon kisi aik shakhs mein jama ho jayen to wo pakka munafiq hai. wo shakhs jo baat karey to jhoot boley, aur jab wada karey, to wada khilaafii karey, aur jab muaahida karey to usey pura na kare. aur jab kisi se ladey to gali galoch par utar aaey aur agar kisi shakhs ke andar un charon aadaton mein se aik hi aadat hai, to iske andar nifaq ki aik aadat hai jab tak ke wo usey chhod na de."
3179,"ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bas yahi Quran Majeed likha aur jo kuchh us waraq mein hai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke Madina Aair pahaadii aur falan (Kudaa) pahaadii ke darmyan tak haram hai. to jisne yahan (deen mein) koi nai cheez dakhil ki ya kisi aisey shakhs ko iske hudood mein panah di to is par Allah ta'alaa, malaaika aur insan sab ki laanat hogi. na uska koi farz qabool aur na nafl qabool hoga aur musalman panah dene mein sab barabar hain. maamooli se maamooli musalman (aurat ya ghulaam) kisi kaafir ko panah de saktey hain. aur jo koi kisi musalman ka kya hua ahad tod daley is par Allah aur malaaika aur insan sab ki laanat hogi, na uski koi farz ibadat qabool hogi aur na nafl! aur jis ghulam ya londi ne apne aaqa apne Malik ki ijazat ke baghair kisi doosrey ko apna Malik bana liya, to is par Allah aur malaaika aur insan sab ki laanat hogi, na uski koi farz ibadat qabool hogi aur na nafl!"
3180,"us waqt tumhara kya haal hoga jab (jiziya aur khiraaj mein se) na tumhen dirham milega aur na Dinar ! is par kisi ne kaha, ke janab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aap kaisey samajhtey hain ke aisa hoga? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha haan us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein Abu-Hurera ki jaan hai. ye sabsey sachey insan (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman hai. logon ne puchha tha ke ye kaisey ho jaeyga ? to aap ne farmaya, jabke Allah aur uske rasool ka ahad (Islaamii hukumat ghair muslimon se unki jaan w maal ki hifazat ke barey mein) todaa janey lagey, to Allah Taala bhi zimmiyon ke dilon ko sakht kar dega aur wo jiziya dena band kar dengey (balke ladney ko muste'ad hongey) ."
3181,"maine abu-Waeil se poochha, kya aap safein ki jang mein maujood they? unhon-ne bayan kya ke yahan (main tha) aur maine Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna tha ke tum log khud apni raey ko ghalat samjho, jo aapas mein ladtey martey ho. maine apne taiin dekha jis din abu-jandal aaya (yani Hudaibiya ke din) agar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hukm pher deta aur ham ne jab kisi museebat mein dar kar talwaarein apne kandhon par rakhein to wo museebat aasan ho gaee. ham ko iska anjam malum ho gaya. magar yahi aik ladai hai (jo sakht mushkil hai iska anjam behtar nahi malum hotaa)."
3182,"ham maqam safain mein derey daley huey they. phir Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur farmaya aey logo ! tum khud apni raey ko ghalat samjho . ham suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, agar hamein ladna hota to us waqt zaroor ladtey . umr (Raziallahu anhu) us mauqe par aaey (yani Hudaibiya mein) aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! kya ham haq par aur wo baatil par nahi hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kyon nahin! umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kya hamarey maqtool jannat main aur unke maqtool jahannam mein nahi jaaeinge? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke kyon nahin! phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ham apne Deen ke mamley mein kyon dabein? kya ham (Madeena) wapas chaley jaaeinge, aur hamarey aur unke darmyan Allah koi faisla nahi karega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ibne-Khattaab! main Allah ka rasool hun aur Allah mujhey kabhi barbad nahi karega.'' iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur unse wahi sawalat kiye, jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abhi kar chukey they. unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain, aur Allah unhein kabhi barbad nahi honey dega. phir sura fateh nazil hui aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko usey aakhir tak padh kar sunaya, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya kya yahi fateh hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! bila shak yahi fateh hai."
3183,"Quraish se jis zamane main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Hudaibiya ki) suleh ki thi, usi muddat mein meri walida (Qutaila) apne bap ( Haris bin mudrik ( ko sath lekar mere paas aaein, wo Islam mein dakhil nahi hui thin. (Urwa ne bayan kya ke) Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne us barey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ya Rasulullah! meri walida aai hui hain aur mujh se raghbat ke sath milnaa chahti hain, to kya main unke sath sila rehmii karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! unke sath sila rehmii kar."
3184,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Umra karna chaha to aap ne Makka mein daakhile ke liye Makka ke logon se ijazat leney ke liye aadmi bhejaa. unhon-ne is shart ke sath (ijaazat di) ke Makka mein teen din se zyada qiyam na karein. hathiyar niyaam mein rakhey baghair dakhil na hon aur (Makka ke) kisi aadmi ko apne sath (Madina ( na ley jayen ( agarche wo jana chahey ( unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir un sharaait ko Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne likhnaa shuru kya aur is tarah ''ye Muhammad Allah ke rasool ke suleh naamaa ki tahreer hai.'' Makka walon ne kaha ke agar ham jaan letey ke aap Allah ke rasool hain to phir aapko roktey hi nahi balke aap par eman latey , isliye tumhen yun likhnaa chahiye, ''ye Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ki suleh naamaa ki tahreer hai''. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah gawah hai ke main Muhammad-bin-Abdullah hun aur Allah gawah hai ke main Allah ka rasool bhi hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) likhnaa nahi jantey they. rawi ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke Rasulullah ka lafz mitaa de. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke Allah ki qism ! ye lafz to main kabhi na mitaaoonga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir mujhey dikhlaao , rawi ne bayan kya ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo lafz dikhaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apne hath se usey mitaa diya. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif le gaey aur (teen) din guzar gaey to Quraish Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke ab apne sathi se kaho ke ab yahan se chaley jayen ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine iska zikr Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya ke haan, chunanche aap wahan se rawaana ho gaey."
3185,"Makka main ( shuru Islam ke zamane main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde ki haalat mein they aur qareeb hi Quraish ke kuchh log baithey huey they. phir Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet oont ki ojhdii laya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peeth par usey daal diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde se apna sar na utha sakey. aakhir Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aaein aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peeth par se us ojhdii ko hataya aur jisne ye harkat ki thi usey bura bhala kaha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi baddua ki ke aey Allah ! Quraish ki is jamat ko pakad. aey Allaah! abu-Jahal bin Hisham , Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba-bin-Rabee'a, Aqba-bin-abii-Mueet, Umayya-bin-Khalaf ya Ubai-bin Khalaf ko barbad kar. phir maine dekha ke ye sab badr ki ladai mein qatl kar diye gaey aur aik kuwein mein unhein daal diya gaya tha. siwa Umayya ya Ubaii ke ke ye shakhs bahut bhari bhar kam tha. jab usey sahaba ne kheenchaa to kuwein mein dalney se pahley hi iske jod jod alag ho gaey."
3186,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din har daghaa baaz ke liye aik jhanda hoga, unmein se aik sahib ne bayan kya ke wo jhanda (iske peechhey ( gaad diya jaeyga aur doosrey sahib ne bayan kya ke usey qiyamat ke din sab dekhengey, iske zariey usey pehchaana jaaeyga.''"
3187,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din har daghaa baaz ke liye aik jhanda hoga, unmein se aik sahib ne bayan kya ke wo jhanda (iske peechhey ( gaad diya jaeyga aur doosrey sahib ne bayan kya ke usey qiyamat ke din sab dekhengey, iske zariey usey pehchaana jaaeyga.''"
3188,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har daghaa baaz ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda hoga jo uski daghaa bazi ki alamat ke taur par (iske peechhey ( gaad diya jaaeyga.''"
3189,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya tha, ab (Makka se) hijrat farz nahi rahi. albatta jihad ki niyat aur jihad ka hukm baqi hai. isliye jab tumhen jihad ke liye nikala jaey to fauran nikal jao aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din ye bhi farmaya tha ke jis din Allah Taala ne aasman aur zameen paida kiye, isi din us Shahar (Makka) ko haram qarar de diya. to ye Shahar Allah ki hurmat ke sath qiyamat tak ke liye haram hi rahega , aur mujh se pahley yahan kisi ke liye ladna jaaiz nahi hua aur mere liye bhi din ke sirf aik ghadi ke liye jaaiz kya gaya. to ab ye Mubarak Shahar Allah Taala ki hurmat ke sath qiyamat tak ke liye haram hai, uski hudood mein na ( kisi darakht ka ( kaantaa todaa jaey, na yahan ke shikar ko sataayaa jaey, aur koi yahan ki giri hui cheez na uthaey siwa us shakhs ke jo (Maalik tak cheez ko pahunchaney ke liye) elaan karey aur na yahan ki harii ghaas kaatii jaey. is par Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ya Rasulullah! izkhir ki ijazat de dijiye. kyonke ye yahan ke sunaaron aur gharon ki chhaton par dalney ke kaam aati hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha izkhir ki ijazat hai."
